  "title": "Old-Fashioned Rhubarb Pie",
  "instructions": {
    "1": "Preheat the oven to 450 degrees F (220 degrees C).",
    "2": "Arrange pie crust in a 9-inch pie pan. Spread rhubarb in an even layer in the bottom of the crust.",
